msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment runs both Prefill and Decode on the same node. The "
"following W8A8 example is suitable for functional validation and image-only "
"online serving on 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) node. The W8A8 version needs "
"`--quantization ascend`."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署在同一节点上运行 Prefill 和 Decode。以下 W8A8 示例适用于在 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) "
"节点上进行功能验证和纯图像在线服务。W8A8 版本需要 `--quantization ascend`。"

msgid "Run the following script to start online serving on one A3 node:"
msgstr "运行以下脚本在一个 A3 节点上启动在线服务："

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If you encounter issues, please refer to the [Public "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) for "
"troubleshooting."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果遇到问题，请参考[公共 "
"FAQ](https://docs.vllm.ai/projects/ascend/en/latest/faqs.html) 进行故障排除。"

msgid "**Key parameters:**"
msgstr "**关键参数：**"

msgid ""
"- `--data-parallel-size 4` and `--tensor-parallel-size 4` map the 16 NPUs on one A3 node into four DP groups, each with TP4.\n"
"- `--enable-expert-parallel` enables expert parallelism for MoE layers. Do not mix MoE tensor parallelism and expert parallelism in the same MoE layer.\n"
"- `--max-model-len` is the maximum input plus output length for a single request. Multimodal inputs consume text tokens and visual tokens, so increase it only when enough KV cache is available.\n"
"- `--max-num-seqs` is the maximum number of active requests scheduled by each DP group. For performance tests, set `--max-num-seqs * --data-parallel-size` greater than or equal to the test concurrency.\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` is the maximum number of tokens processed in one scheduler step. A larger value can improve prefill efficiency but consumes more activation memory.\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` controls how much HBM vLLM can use to calculate KV cache capacity. A higher value increases KV cache size but can trigger OOM if runtime memory is higher than the profile run.\n"
"- `--quantization ascend` enables Ascend quantization for the W8A8 model. Remove this option when deploying the BF16 model.\n"
"- `--limit-mm-per-prompt.image 1` and `--limit-mm-per-prompt.video 0` reserve multimodal capacity for one image per request and disable video inputs to save memory.\n"
"- `--mm-processor-cache-gb 0` disables the multimodal processor cache. Increase it only when your workload benefits from reused media preprocessing and you have enough host memory.\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` enables full decode ACLGraph replay to reduce dispatch overhead."
msgstr ""
"- `--data-parallel-size 4` 和 `--tensor-parallel-size 4` 将一个 A3 节点上的 16 个 NPU 映射为四个 DP 组，每个组内使用 TP4。\n"
"- `--enable-expert-parallel` 为 MoE 层启用专家并行。不要在同一个 MoE 层中混合使用 MoE 张量并行和专家并行。\n"
"- `--max-model-len` 是单个请求的最大输入加输出长度。多模态输入会消耗文本 token 和视觉 token，因此仅在拥有足够 KV 缓存时增加此值。\n"
"- `--max-num-seqs` 是每个 DP 组调度的最大并发请求数。对于性能测试，请确保 `--max-num-seqs * --data-parallel-size` 大于或等于测试并发数。\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` 是单个调度步骤中处理的最大 token 数。较大的值可以提高 prefill 效率，但会消耗更多激活内存。\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` 控制 vLLM 可用于计算 KV 缓存容量的 HBM 比例。较高的值会增加 KV 缓存大小，但如果运行时内存高于 profile 运行时的内存，则可能触发 OOM。\n"
"- `--quantization ascend` 为 W8A8 模型启用 Ascend 量化。部署 BF16 模型时请移除该选项。\n"
"- `--limit-mm-per-prompt.image 1` 和 `--limit-mm-per-prompt.video 0` 为每个请求预留一张图像的多模态处理能力，并禁用视频输入以节省内存。\n"
"- `--mm-processor-cache-gb 0` 禁用多模态处理器缓存。仅当您的工作负载受益于重复使用的媒体预处理且拥有足够的主机内存时，才增加此值。\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 启用完整的 Decode ACLGraph 重放以减少调度开销。"

msgid "### 5.2 Multi-Node Deployment with MP (Recommended for BF16)"
msgstr "### 5.2 使用 MP 的多节点部署（推荐用于 BF16）"

msgid ""
"Multi-node MP deployment uses vLLM data parallelism across nodes and tensor "
"parallelism within each node. It is recommended for the BF16 model on 2 "
"Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) nodes, or for long-context validation where one node "
"does not provide enough HBM headroom."
msgstr ""
"多节点MP部署在节点间使用vLLM数据并行，在节点内使用张量并行。推荐在2个Atlas 800 A2（64G x "
"8）节点上部署BF16模型，或用于单个节点HBM空间不足的长上下文验证场景。"

msgid ""
"Assume you have 2 Atlas 800 A2 nodes and want to deploy "
"`Qwen3-VL-235B-A22B-Instruct-w8a8-QuaRot` across them. Replace `nic_name`, "
"`local_ip`, and `node0_ip` with the actual network interface and IP "
"addresses in your environment."
msgstr ""
"假设您有2个Atlas 800 "
"A2节点，并希望跨节点部署`Qwen3-VL-235B-A22B-Instruct-w8a8-QuaRot`。请将`nic_name`、`local_ip`和`node0_ip`替换为您环境中的实际网络接口和IP地址。"

msgid "Run the following script on node 0."
msgstr "在节点0上运行以下脚本。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If node 1 cannot join the service or HCCL initialization "
"times out, refer to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication) and "
"[Public FAQs](../../faqs.md). Make sure the network interface names, IP "
"addresses, and RPC ports are consistent across nodes."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果节点1无法加入服务或HCCL初始化超时，请参考[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-"
"multi-node-communication)和[常见问题解答](../../faqs.md)。确保各节点的网络接口名称、IP地址和RPC端口一致。"

msgid "Run the following script on node 1."
msgstr "在节点1上运行以下脚本。"

msgid ""
"If the service starts successfully, the following information is displayed "
"on node 0:"
msgstr "如果服务启动成功，节点0上将显示以下信息："

msgid "**Key parameters for MP deployment:**"
msgstr "**MP部署的关键参数：**"

msgid ""
"- `--data-parallel-size` is the global DP size across all nodes. In the example, 2 DP ranks are used.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-size-local` is the number of DP ranks on the current node. In the example, each A2 node has 1 local DP rank.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank` is the first DP rank on the current node. Node 0 starts from 0 by default, and node 1 starts from 1.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` must point to the master DP node. Use node 0 `local_ip` on node 0 and `node0_ip` on other nodes.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-rpc-port` is the DP RPC port. Use the same value on all nodes and ensure the port is available.\n"
"- `--api-server-count` controls how many API server processes are started on the master node.\n"
"- `--headless` starts a worker node without exposing an API server. Use it on non-master nodes.\n"
"- `--tensor-parallel-size 8` maps one TP group to the 8 NPUs on each A2 node.\n"
"- `HCCL_IF_IP`, `GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`, `TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`, and `HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME` bind HCCL, Gloo, and TP communication to the selected network."
msgstr ""
"- `--data-parallel-size` 是所有节点的全局DP大小。示例中使用2个DP rank。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-size-local` 是当前节点上的DP rank数量。示例中每个A2节点有1个本地DP rank。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank` 是当前节点上的起始DP rank。节点0默认从0开始，节点1从1开始。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` 必须指向主DP节点。节点0使用`local_ip`，其他节点使用`node0_ip`。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-rpc-port` 是DP RPC端口。所有节点使用相同值，并确保端口可用。\n"
"- `--api-server-count` 控制主节点上启动的API服务器进程数量。\n"
"- `--headless` 启动一个不暴露API服务器的工作节点。在非主节点上使用。\n"
"- `--tensor-parallel-size 8` 将一个TP组映射到每个A2节点上的8个NPU。\n"
"- `HCCL_IF_IP`、`GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`、`TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`和`HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME`将HCCL、Gloo和TP通信绑定到所选网络。"

msgid "### 5.3 Multi-Node PD Separation Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.3 多节点PD分离部署"

msgid ""
"PD disaggregation separates Prefill and Decode into different service "
"groups. Prefill nodes process large prompt chunks, Decode nodes serve token "
"generation, and a proxy forwards requests between them. This mode is "
"suitable for production serving scenarios where prefill and decode resource "
"ratios need to be tuned separately."
msgstr ""
"PD分离将Prefill和Decode划分为不同的服务组。Prefill节点处理大型提示块，Decode节点负责token生成，代理在两者之间转发请求。此模式适用于需要分别调整prefill和decode资源比例的生产服务场景。"

msgid ""
"We recommend using Mooncake for deployment. Refer to "
"[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) for the "
"general PD disaggregation workflow and request forwarding setup."
msgstr ""
"我们推荐使用Mooncake进行部署。请参考[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)了解通用PD分离工作流和请求转发设置。"

msgid ""
"The following example matches the validated A3 two-node topology for "
"`Qwen3-VL-235B-A22B-Instruct-w8a8-QuaRot`:"
msgstr "以下示例匹配已验证的A3双节点拓扑，适用于`Qwen3-VL-235B-A22B-Instruct-w8a8-QuaRot`："

msgid ""
"- 1 Prefill node: 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16), DP2 + TP8 + EP.\n"
"- 1 Decode node: 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16), DP4 + TP4 + EP + full decode ACLGraph."
msgstr ""
"- 1个Prefill节点：1个Atlas 800 A3（64G x 16），DP2 + TP8 + EP。\n"
"- 1个Decode节点：1个Atlas 800 A3（64G x 16），DP4 + TP4 + EP + 全量decode ACLGraph。"

msgid "#### 5.3.1 Prefill Node"
msgstr "#### 5.3.1 Prefill节点"

msgid "Create `run_p.sh` on the prefill node."
msgstr "在prefill节点上创建`run_p.sh`。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If the prefill service is not ready for a long time, "
"check whether the model path is shared, all 16 NPUs are visible, and the "
"Mooncake `kv_port` is available."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果prefill服务长时间未就绪，请检查模型路径是否共享、所有16个NPU是否可见以及Mooncake的`kv_port`是否可用。"

msgid "#### 5.3.2 Decode Node"
msgstr "#### 5.3.2 Decode节点"

msgid "Create `run_d.sh` on the decode node."
msgstr "在decode节点上创建`run_d.sh`。"

msgid "**Key parameters for PD disaggregation:**"
msgstr "**PD分离的关键参数：**"

msgid ""
"- Prefill uses `--data-parallel-size 2`, `--data-parallel-size-local 2`, and `--tensor-parallel-size 8`.\n"
"- Decode uses `--data-parallel-size 4`, `--data-parallel-size-local 4`, and `--tensor-parallel-size 4`.\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` is set to 8192 on both sides in this validation topology. Increase the prefill value only if activation memory is sufficient.\n"
"- `--kv-transfer-config` sets the Mooncake connector. `kv_role` is `kv_producer` on prefill and `kv_consumer` on decode.\n"
"- `kv_connector_extra_config.prefill.dp_size/tp_size` and `decode.dp_size/tp_size` must match the actual global DP and TP layout.\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` disables prefix caching. For PD disaggregation, first validate the service without prefix caching before enabling additional cache features.\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` is recommended on decode nodes to reduce decode dispatch overhead."
msgstr ""
"- Prefill使用`--data-parallel-size 2`、`--data-parallel-size-local 2`和`--tensor-parallel-size 8`。\n"
"- Decode使用`--data-parallel-size 4`、`--data-parallel-size-local 4`和`--tensor-parallel-size 4`。\n"
"- 在此验证拓扑中，两侧的`--max-num-batched-tokens`均设置为8192。仅在激活内存充足时增加prefill的值。\n"
"- `--kv-transfer-config`设置Mooncake连接器。`kv_role`在prefill上为`kv_producer`，在decode上为`kv_consumer`。\n"
"- `kv_connector_extra_config.prefill.dp_size/tp_size`和`decode.dp_size/tp_size`必须与实际全局DP和TP布局匹配。\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching`禁用前缀缓存。对于PD分离，在启用额外缓存功能之前，请先在不使用前缀缓存的情况下验证服务。\n"
"- 建议在decode节点上使用`--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'`以减少decode调度开销。"

